reviewText: Tracey will lead you and her team of 2 through a 50 minute workout using a variety of equipment: med ball or dumbbell, Swiss ball, Bosu, and step. Exercises are familiar ones with short reps: sit-ups, push-ups, planks.  That being said, I'd recommend it for beginner-intermediate.  It's not intensive at all, so if you want a light core focused workout day, this is an option.
